{"tid":911833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可憐小隻馬遭癡漢戴套性侵　還被怨會傳病","createTime":"2018-11-22T08:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T08:56:32.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"14dc7a2a3ed9efc603fe2612f43d72c109412404","tid":911833,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"美國佛羅里達州一隻小隻馬「傑克G」(Jackie G)，慘遭21歲癡漢薩爾多(Nicholas Sardo)多次性侵，薩爾多還嫌牠會傳染疾病，因此都會戴保險套做愛。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，這隻迷你馬是薩爾多一名親戚所養，但薩爾多卻多次對牠性侵，曾有女子直擊薩爾多在家族成員的牧場裡，性侵傑克G。另外還有一名女子也目擊過薩爾多的猥褻行為，並向女子承認性侵犯行。目前薩爾多已被警方逮捕，他承認性侵傑克G，一周至少性侵4次，而他擔心會被傑克G傳染病，因此都會帶套做愛。<br />\n <br />\n目前薩爾多被控4項虐待動物以及與動物性交等罪名，但警方未公布小隻馬的傷勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hBmydTt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhBmydTt.png&h=a64c23b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vRS17dx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvRS17dx.png&h=054c19e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"173a4517f08983dfbe22d252edbc8bbcac3eff81","tid":911833,"uid":162316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:43:21.000Z","msg":"隻馬仔好得意"},{"pid":"6f471ceb0cfd0a8b4e29b4767b008712894ad621","tid":911833,"uid":198932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &lt;-- 隻馬個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af682ab9a19c7ee917d07baccf589980e7d249f","tid":911833,"uid":186692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"乜屌騾仔閪 要用袋嘅咩？"},{"pid":"4b6e11a9d2a5eaa8df3e70028ed268c35947a735","tid":911833,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"受過咩刺激先會搞動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國同香港社會都好少會有依啲新聞"},{"pid":"3971bffea09b385cc1644c6de36d1b2db010dd0d","tid":911833,"uid":136415,"like":0